==过境免签==
任何人过境少于24小时，不离开机场过境区，则不需要过境签证。以下人士具有过境免签资格：<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.immigration.govt.nz/migrant/stream/visit/transit/ |title=过境 |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2014-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702030153/http://www.immigration.govt.nz/migrant/stream/visit/transit/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
