==库克群岛==
所有前往[[库克群岛|库克群岛]]的公民（无论国籍），均可以免签证入境停留31天。以旅游为目的入境的，则停留期限可延长至6个月。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?FullText=1&COUNTRY=CK&SECTION=VI&SUBSECTION=00&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C |title=签证资料 |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2019-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219012712/https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?FullText=1 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

